 >- (rw_tac int_ss [INT_ABS]
     >- (qpat_x_assum `~(0 <= i)` kall_tac
         >> qpat_x_assum `i < &(2 ** (bits - 1))` kall_tac
         >> `2n ** bits = 2n ** (bits - 1) + 2n ** (bits - 1)`
